"Bad bad bad idea," said Brown, on the verge of tears.
"My hair has been like this for about a month now. It's not my choice," she added.
Brown said she had tried various lotions and products, including shampoo and coconut oil, to break the glue but without success.
Her story has gone viral, with internet users offering numerous solutions for her sticky situation.Â 
